    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of exceptional caliber. This example remains in showroom-grade condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine cabin, confirms its status as a premier selection for the discerning collector. A rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that mirrors its original factory delivery state.",
